#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmymoney; for the first time"
msgstr "Prva uporaba &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running &kmymoney; for the first time"
msgstr "Ko zaženemo &kmymoney; prvič"

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshots may differ"
msgstr "Posnetki zaslona se lahko razlikujejo"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you run &kmymoney;, it might not look exactly like the screenshots in "
"this manual. Many details, such as fonts, colors, and icons, can be "
"customized, using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item or the &kde; &systemsettings; application, depending on your operating "
"system or distribution."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kmymoney;, morda ne bo videti povsem tako kot posnetki zaslona "
"v tem priročniku. Veliko podrobnosti, kot so pisave, barve in ikone, je "
"mogoče prilagoditi z uporabo menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kmymoney;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali &kde; &systemsettings; "
"aplikacije, odvisno od vašega operacijskega sistema ali distribucije."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Main Window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kmymoney; main window consists of four major parts"
msgstr "&kmymoney; glavno okno je sestavljeno iz štirih večjih delov"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "A. The menu bar"
msgstr "A. Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "B. The toolbar"
msgstr "B. Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "C. The View selector"
msgstr "C. Izbirnik pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "D. The view"
msgstr "D. Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menu and toolbar provide access to the features of &kmymoney; and allow "
"you to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile\">Create a new data file,</link> "
"open an existing data file, or configure how &kmymoney; operates. The "
"toolbar can be configured to show icons for the operations you use most "
"frequently."
msgstr ""
"Meni in orodna vrstica omogočata dostop do funkcij &kmymoney; in vam "
"omogočajo, da <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile\">ustvarite novo podatkovno "
"datoteko,</link> odprete obstoječo podatkovno datoteko ali konfigurirate, "
"kako &kmymoney; deluje. Orodno vrstico je mogoče konfigurirati tako, da "
"prikaže ikone za operacije, ki jih najpogosteje uporabljate."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side of the main window, the View Selector consists of at least "
"eleven icons with optional labels, depending upon the software provided by "
"your system, as some features can be included or excluded when the program "
"is compiled. More icons could be added by various plugins. By clicking one "
"of the icon, the view window on the right hand side is loaded with the "
"appropriate view of your financial data. Each view provides a unique "
"representation of your financial situation and allows you to view or edit "
"the information shown."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani glavnega okna je izbirnik pogleda sestavljen iz vsaj enajstih "
"ikon z neobveznimi oznakami, odvisno od programske opreme, ki jo nudi vaš "
"sistem, saj je mogoče nekatere funkcije vključiti ali izključiti, ko je "
"program preveden. Več ikon bi lahko dodali različni vtičniki. S klikom na "
"eno od ikon se okno pogleda na desni strani naloži z ustreznim pogledom "
"vaših finančnih podatkov. Vsak pogled zagotavlja edinstveno predstavitev "
"vašega finančnega stanja in vam omogoča ogled ali urejanje prikazanih "
"informacij."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Selector may contain the following icons"
msgstr "Izbirnik pogleda lahko vsebuje naslednje ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"home_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Home View</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Home: a configurable "
"overview of your current financial situation (or an introduction page when "
"no data file is open.)"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"home_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Domači pogled</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Dom: Nastavljiv "
"pregled vašega trenutnega finančnega položaja (ali uvodna stran, kadar ni "
"odprte nobene podatkovne datoteke)."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"institutions_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Institutions View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Institutions: your institutions and accounts displayed in a "
"hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"institutions_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled institucij</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Institucije: Vse vaše institucije in računi, prikazane v hierarhiji."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"accounts_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Accounts View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"Accounts: your accounts displayed in a hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"accounts_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled računov</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Računi: Vsi vaši računi prikazani v hierarhiji."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"schedule_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Schedules View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Scheduled transactions: your recurring payments, income, and "
"transfers."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"schedule_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Ogled časovnih razporedov</phrase> </textobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Načrtovane transakcije: vaša ponavljajoča se "
"plačila, prihodki in prenosi."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"categories_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Categories View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Categories: special accounts that provide a means for you to group "
"associated transactions."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"categories_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled kategorij</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Katagorije: Posebni računi, ki vam omogočajo združevanje povezanih "
"transakcij."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"mail-tagged."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Tags View</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Tags: special accounts "
"that provide an additional means similar to Categories for you to group "
"associated transactions."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"mail-tagged."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Pogled značk</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Značke: Posebni "
"računi, ki nudijo dodatne načine za združevanje kategorij transakcij."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"payees_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Payees View</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Payees: your payees - "
"the people and organizations you pay money to or receive money from."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"payees_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Ogled prejemnikov "
"plačil</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Prejemniki "
"plačil: vaši prejemniki plačil – ljudje in organizacije, ki jim plačujete "
"denar ali od katerih prejemate denar."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Ledgers View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"Ledgers: your transactions in each account."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"ledgers_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled glavne knjige</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Glavne knjige: vaše transakcije na vsakem računu."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"investments_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Investments View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Investments: your portfolio summary"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"investments_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled investicij</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Investicije: Izvleček vašega portfelja"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"reports_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Reports View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"Reports: a collection of various, customizable displays of your financial "
"data."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"reports_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled poročil</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Poročila: zbirka različnih, prilagodljivih prikazov vaših finančnih "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"budgets_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Budgets View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"Budgets: your budgets."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"budgets_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled proračunov</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Proračuni: vaši proračuni."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"forecast_view_icon.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Forecast View</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> "
"Forecast: forecast of the balances of your accounts and categories."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"forecast_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> "
"<phrase>Pogled napovedi</phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </"
"guiicon> Napovedi: Ta pogled nudi napoved stanj vaših računov in kategorij."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"outbox_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Outbox View</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Outbox: a display "
"provided by the KBanking plugin to provide feedback on running processes."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"outbox_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> <textobject> <phrase>Ogled pošiljanja</"
"phrase> </textobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Izhodna pošta: zaslon, "
"ki ga nudi vtičnik KBanking za zagotavljanje povratnih informacij o tekočih "
"procesih."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember that some of these may not be present on your system; it depends on "
"how your copy of &kmymoney; was configured and built."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da nekateri od teh morda niso prisotni v vašem sistemu; odvisno "
"od tega, kako je bila vaša kopija &kmymoney; konfigurirana in izdelana."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new file"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje nove datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; keeps all the data about your finances in a file. As was stated "
"in <link linkend=\"makingmostof.basicaccounting.personalaccounts\">Defining "
"the accounts (personal records)</link>, you can keep more than one set of "
"accounts, but the data for each will be kept in a separate file, and "
"&kmymoney; can only have one file open at a time. See the chapter on <link "
"linkend=\"details.formats\">File Formats</link> for more details about "
"&kmymoney;'s data files."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; hrani vse podatke o vaših financah v datoteki. Kot je bilo "
"navedeno v <link linkend=\"makingmostof.basicaccounting.personalaccounts"
"\">Določanje računov (osebnih evidenc)</link>, lahko obdržite več kot en niz "
"računov, vendar bodo podatki za vsakega shranjeni v ločeni datoteki in "
"&kmymoney; ima lahko naenkrat odprto samo eno datoteko. Glejte poglavje o "
"<link linkend=\"details.formats\">Oblikah datotek</link> za več podrobnosti "
"o podatkovnih datotekah &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to that data file with all the financial data for that set of "
"accounts, &kmymoney; uses additional files to store data regarding "
"configuration settings and display preferences. The exact location of these "
"files depends on your specific Operating System or Distribution."
msgstr ""
"Poleg te podatkovne datoteke z vsemi finančnimi podatki za ta niz računov, "
"&kmymoney; uporablja dodatne datoteke za shranjevanje podatkov v zvezi s "
"nastavitvami konfiguracije in nastavitvami prikaza. Natančna lokacija teh "
"datotek je odvisna od vašega operacijskega sistema ali distribucije."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new file you can either select the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or choose the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"new.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> <guilabel>new</"
"guilabel> icon from the toolbar. In addition, if the main welcome page is "
"displayed, you can also select the first link: <quote>Get started and setup "
"accounts.</quote>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo datoteko, lahko izberete menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali izberete <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref =\"new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> <guilabel>nova</guilabel> ikona v orodni vrstici. Poleg tega, če je "
"prikazana glavna pozdravna stran, lahko izberete tudi prvo povezavo: "
"<quote>Začnite in nastavite račune.</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; will then open the <quote>New File Setup Wizard</quote> which "
"will guide you through the process of creating the file."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; bo nato odprl <quote>Čarovnik za nastavitev nove datoteke</"
"quote>, ki vas bo vodil skozi postopek ustvarjanja datoteke."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Personal Data Page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Stran z osebnimi podatki</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Personal Data Page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stran z osebnimi podatki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any information entered hereon the <guilabel>Personal Data</guilabel> page "
"is used only to personalize your file. All these fields are optional, so you "
"can use &kmymoney; without entering any information now. In the future, this "
"information may be used in some reports and for online banking. If "
"&kmymoney; requires any personal information in future releases and finds "
"none, you will be prompted to enter the relevant data then."
msgstr ""
"Vsi podatki, vneseni tukaj na strani <guilabel>Osebni podatki</guilabel>, se "
"uporabljajo samo za prilagajanje vaše datoteke. Vsa ta polja so neobvezna, "
"zato lahko uporabite &kmymoney; ne da bi zdaj vnesli kakršne koli "
"informacije. V prihodnosti bodo te informacije morda uporabljene v nekaterih "
"poročilih in za spletno bančništvo. Če &kmymoney; zahteva kakršne koli "
"osebne podatke v prihodnjih izdajah in jih ne najde, boste takrat pozvani, "
"da vnesete ustrezne podatke."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you have an address for yourself stored in the &kaddressbook;, the "
"button <guibutton>Load from Addressbook</guibutton> is enabled and pressing "
"it imports all information into &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Če imate svoj naslov shranjen v &kaddressbook;, je gumb <guibutton>Naloži iz "
"imenika</guibutton> omogočen in s pritiskom nanj uvozite vse informacije v "
"&kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have completed entering data, press <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z vnosom podatkov, pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to change any of this information in the future, you can access "
"this form with the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Personal "
"Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če boste morali v prihodnosti spremeniti katerega od teh podatkov, lahko do "
"tega obrazca dostopate z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Osebni podatki...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; supports multiple currencies. To set your base currency (the "
"currency you use day to day and which will be used for your reports,) select "
"the appropriate entry from the list provided and press <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton>. A default will be selected based upon your locale settings, but "
"you can easily choose a different currency, if appropriate for you situation."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; podpira več valut. Če želite nastaviti svojo osnovno valuto "
"(valuto, ki jo uporabljate vsak dan in ki bo uporabljena za vaša poročila), "
"izberite ustrezen vnos s ponujenega seznama in pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>. Privzeta vrednost bo izbrana na podlagi vaših področnih "
"nastavitev, vendar lahko preprosto izberete drugo valuto, če je primerna za "
"vašo situacijo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base currency selection Page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro osnovne valute"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base currency selection page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro osnovne valute"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this example, US Dollar has been selected as the base currency."
msgstr "V tem primeru je bil kot osnovna valuta izbran ameriški dolar."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you click <guibutton>Next</guibutton>, the following page allows you "
"to create an initial account. For the typical &kmymoney; user this is a "
"checking account."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>, vam naslednja stran omogoča "
"ustvarjanje začetnega računa. Za tipičnega uporabnika &kmymoney; je to "
"tekoči (transakcijski) račun."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking account creation Page"
msgstr "Stran za ustvarjanje tekočega računa"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking account creation page"
msgstr "Stran za ustvarjanje tekočega računa"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the account and a possible account or reference number "
"assigned by the institution managing the account. The name is arbitrary, and "
"is simply how the account will be referenced and displayed by &kmymoney;. "
"Enter the opening date and the opening balance of the account. For example, "
"if you want to use &kmymoney; to manage all your finances as of 2008-01-01, "
"then enter the balance of the account at the beginning of this date. The "
"number can possibly be obtained from a paper statement. You may also enter "
"the name and the bank code of the institution. The latter, known as the "
"routing number in the US or the sort code in the UK, is optional and only "
"required for online banking purposes, but it may also be helpful when "
"importing bank statements in some of the formats supported (OFX, QFX.)"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime računa in morebitni račun ali referenčno številko, ki jo dodeli "
"institucija, ki vodi račun. Ime je poljubno in je preprosto način, na "
"katerega se bo račun skliceval in prikazoval &kmymoney;. Vnesite datum "
"odprtja in začetno stanje na računu. Na primer, če želite uporabljati "
"&kmymoney; za upravljanje vseh vaših financ od 01. 1. 2008, nato vnesite "
"stanje na računu na začetku tega datuma. Številko je mogoče dobiti iz "
"papirnatega izpiska. Vnesete lahko tudi ime in kodo banke institucije. "
"Slednja, znana kot usmerjevalna številka v ZDA ali razvrstitvena koda v "
"Združenem kraljestvu, je izbirna in potrebna le za namene spletnega "
"bančništva, lahko pa je tudi v pomoč pri uvozu bančnih izpiskov v nekaterih "
"podprtih formatih (OFX, QFX. )"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you don't want to setup an initial account or don't have a checking "
"account, just uncheck the checkbox."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da ne želite nastaviti začetnega računa ali nimate tekočega "
"računa, počistite potrditveno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Once finished, press <guibutton>Next</guibutton> to proceed."
msgstr "Ko končate, pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> za nadaljevanje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account template selection Page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro predloge računa"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account template selection page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro predloge računa"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the appropriate country and account template(s). Each template "
"provides a different set of categories for organizing your finances. "
"Multiple templates, even from different countries, can be selected using a "
"combination of &Ctrl; and &Shift; together with the &LMB;. The account "
"hierarchy to be setup will be shown in a preview part of the wizard. In case "
"you cannot find a template that suits your needs, don't select a template at "
"this time, and you can manually set up categories later."
msgstr ""
"Izberite ustrezno državo in predloge računa. Vsaka predloga nudi drugačen "
"nabor kategorij za organiziranje vaših financ. Več predlog, tudi iz "
"različnih držav, lahko izberete s kombinacijo &Ctrl; in &Shift; skupaj z "
"&LMB;. Hierarhija računa, ki jo želite nastaviti, bo prikazana v delu "
"čarovnika za predogled. Če ne najdete predloge, ki bi ustrezala vašim "
"potrebam, trenutno ne izberite predloge in lahko pozneje ročno nastavite "
"kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once finished with the template selection press <guibutton>Next</guibutton> "
"to proceed."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z izbiro predloge, pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> za "
"nadaljevanje."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the final page of the wizard. If you select the checkbox "
"<quote>Configure preferences after finishing the wizard</quote>, the "
"application settings dialog will be displayed after you have completed the "
"account setup wizard."
msgstr ""
"To je zadnja stran čarovnika. Če izberete potrditveno polje "
"<quote>Konfiguriraj nastavitve po koncu čarovnika</quote>, se bo pogovorno "
"okno z nastavitvami aplikacije prikazalo, ko boste dokončali čarovnika za "
"nastavitev računa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: firsttime.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename selection Page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro imena datoteke"

#. Tag: phrase
#: firsttime.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename selection page"
msgstr "Stran za izbiro imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At this point, clicking <quote>Finish</quote> will start the <quote>Save "
"storage as...</quote> dialog, where you choose the type of storage (XML, "
"possibly with encryption, or SQL) and specify the details of that storage "
"method, such as file name and location or sql database details. See the "
"<link linkend=\"details.formats\">File Formats</link> and <link linkend="
"\"details.database\">File Formats</link> chapters for more information about "
"each storage type."
msgstr ""
"Na tej točki s klikom na <quote>Dokončaj</quote> se odpre pogovorno okno "
"<quote>Shrani pomnilnik kot...</quote>, kjer izberete vrsto pomnilnika (XML, "
"po možnosti s šifriranjem ali SQL) in določite podrobnosti tega načina "
"shranjevanja, kot sta ime in lokacija datoteke ali podrobnosti baze podatkov "
"sql. Glejte poglavji <link linkend=\"details.formats\">Oblike datotek</link> "
"in <link linkend=\"details.database\">Oblike datotek</link> za več "
"informacij o vsaki vrsti shranjevanja."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating accounts"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje računov"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are multiple ways you can create an account:"
msgstr "Račun lahko ustvarite na več načinov:"

#. Tag: term
#: firsttime.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the menu"
msgstr "Z uporabo menija"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create an account using the menu select the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Accounts</guimenu><guimenuitem>New account</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti račun z uporabo menija, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Računi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novi račun</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: firsttime.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Accounts View"
msgstr "Uporaba pogleda računov"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create an account using the Accounts View, click the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"accounts_view.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> accounts icon "
"in the View Selector to display the Accounts View. Right-click either the "
"Asset tree icon or the Liability tree icon in the display and select "
"<guimenuitem>New account</guimenuitem> from the popup menu. The Asset tree "
"holds all of your accounts that are assets, such as savings and investments. "
"The Liability tree holds all of your accounts that represent money you owe, "
"such as loans and credit cards. These and all the other account types are "
"discussed in more detail in the <link linkend=\"details.accounts\">Accounts "
"Chapter.</link>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti račun s pogledom računov, kliknite ikono računov "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"accounts_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> v "
"izbirniku pogleda, da prikažete pogled računov. Z desno tipko miške kliknite "
"ikono drevesa imetij ali ikono drevesa obveznosti na zaslonu in v pojavnem "
"meniju izberite <guimenuitem>Novi račun</guimenuitem>. Drevo imetij vsebuje "
"vse vaše račune, ki so imetja, kot so prihranki in naložbe. Drevo obveznosti "
"vsebuje vse vaše račune, ki predstavljajo denar, ki ga dolgujete, kot so "
"posojila in kreditne kartice. Te in vse druge vrste računov so podrobneje "
"obravnavane v <link linkend=\"details.accounts\">poglavju o računih.</link>"

#. Tag: term
#: firsttime.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the toolbar"
msgstr "Z uporabo orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guibutton>New Account...</guibutton> button is displayed on the "
"toolbar, you can click it to create an account."
msgstr ""
"Če je v orodni vrstici prikazan gumb <guibutton>Novi račun...</guibutton>, "
"ga lahko kliknete, da ustvarite račun."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that &kmymoney; uses context menus throughout the whole application. If "
"you find yourself stuck trying to figure out how to do something, try "
"clicking the &RMB; where you would expect to see a feature."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da &kmymoney; uporablja kontekstne menije v celotni aplikaciji. "
"Če ste obtičali pri iskanju, kako nekaj narediti, poskusite klikniti &RMB; "
"kjer bi pričakovali, da boste videli funkcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creating a new account by any of the above methods opens the <emphasis>New "
"Account Wizard</emphasis>. This wizard will take you step by step through "
"the process of creating an account, gathering the required information at "
"each step. To navigate through the pages click <guibutton>Next</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Back</guibutton>. A full description of creating accounts can "
"be found in the <link linkend=\"details.accounts\">Accounts</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Če ustvarite nov račun s katero koli od zgornjih metod, se odpre "
"<emphasis>čarovnik za nov račun</emphasis>. Ta čarovnik vas bo korak za "
"korakom popeljal skozi postopek ustvarjanja računa in pri vsakem koraku "
"zbral potrebne informacije. Za krmarjenje po straneh kliknite "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> in <guibutton>Nazaj</guibutton>. Popoln opis "
"ustvarjanja računov najdete v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.accounts"
"\">Računi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that one or more accounts exist in &kmymoney;, your account summary is "
"shown in the Home View. You can create transactions manually in the <link "
"linkend=\"details.ledgers\">Ledgers</link> View, or set up automatic "
"transactions through the <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Schedules</"
"link> View."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko obstaja en ali več računov v &kmymoney;, je povzetek vašega računa "
"prikazan v domačem pogledu. Transakcije lahko ustvarite ročno v pogledu "
"<link linkend=\"details.ledgers\">Glavne knjige</link> ali nastavite "
"samodejne transakcije v pogledu <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Časovni "
"razporedi</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scheduled transactions"
msgstr "Načrtovane transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">scheduled transaction</link>, "
"sometimes called a schedule or a recurring transaction, is a transaction "
"that occurs one or more times at a specified interval over a certain period "
"of time. A typical example is your pay check that you receive every week or "
"month, or a utility bill you pay every month. Rather than having to enter "
"the transaction details each time you get paid, you can instruct &kmymoney; "
"to create a schedule that will enter a transaction for you when you get paid."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"details.schedules\">Časovno načrtovana transakcija</link>, "
"včasih imenovana planirana ali ponavljajoča se transakcija, je transakcija, "
"ki se zgodi enkrat ali večkrat v določenem intervalu v določenem časovnem "
"obdobju. Tipičen primer je vaša plača, ki jo prejmete vsak teden ali mesec, "
"ali račun za komunalne storitve, ki ga plačate vsak mesec. Namesto da bi "
"morali vsakič, ko prejmete plačilo, vnašati podatke o transakciji, lahko "
"naročite &kmymoney; da ustvarite časovni plan, ki bo namesto vas vnesel "
"transakcijo, ko boste prejeli plačilo."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To maintain your <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">schedules</link>, click "
"the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"schedule_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> Scheduled transaction icon in the View Selector."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vzdrževati svoje <link linkend=\"details.schedules\">časovne "
"razporede</link>, kliknite "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"schedule_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Ikono "
"načrtovane transakcije v izbirniku pogleda."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "Kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To maintain your <link linkend=\"details.categories\">categories</link>, "
"click the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"categories_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> Categories icon in the View Selector."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vzdrževati svoje <link linkend=\"details.categories\">kategorije</"
"link>, kliknite <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"categories_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> Ikono kategorij v izbirniku pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A full description of this topic can be found in the <link linkend=\"details."
"categories\">Categories</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Celoten opis te teme je na voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"details."
"categories\">Kategorije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Značke"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To maintain your <link linkend=\"details.tags\">tags</link>, click the "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-tagged."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Tags "
"icon in the View Selector."
msgstr ""
"Za vzdrževanje <link linkend=\"details.tags\">značk</link> kliknite "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"mail-tagged."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject ></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ikono "
"značk v izbirniku pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A more detailed description of this topic can be found in the <link linkend="
"\"details.tags\">Tags</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejši opis te teme je na voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.tags"
"\">Značke</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payees"
msgstr "Prejemniki plačil"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To maintain your <link linkend=\"details.payees\">payees</link>, click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"payees_view."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Payees "
"icon in the View Selector."
msgstr ""
"Za vzdrževanje vaših <link linkend=\"details.payees\">prejemnikov plačil</"
"link>, kliknite <guiicon><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"payees_view.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> Ikono prejemnikov plačil v izbirniku pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A more detailed description of this topic can be found in the <link linkend="
"\"details.payees\">Payees</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejši opis te teme je na voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"details."
"payees\">Prejemniki plačil</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing financial data from other applications"
msgstr "Uvoz finančnih podatkov iz drugih aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you currently use another financial manager application, it is very "
"likely that &kmymoney; can import much or all of the data from that program, "
"as long as they can be exported or saved in a format &kmymoney; understands. "
"The most common of these is the Quicken Interchange Format (QIF). Most "
"financial programs can export this format, although the different "
"applications' methods of exporting QIF is not discussed here for brevity."
msgstr ""
"Če trenutno uporabljate drugo aplikacijo finančnega upravljalnika, je zelo "
"verjetno, da &kmymoney; lahko uvozi večino ali vse podatke iz tega programa, "
"če jih je mogoče izvoziti ali shraniti v formatu, ki ga &kmymoney; razume. "
"Najpogostejši med njimi je Quicken Interchange Format (QIF). Večina "
"finančnih programov lahko izvozi ta format, čeprav tukaj zaradi jedrnatosti "
"ne obravnavamo načinov izvoza QIF različnih aplikacij."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A full description of importing data in this format can be found in the "
"<link linkend=\"details.impexp.qifimp\">QIF Import</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Celoten opis uvoza podatkov v tej obliki je na voljo v razdelku <link "
"linkend=\"details.impexp.qifimp\">Uvoz QIF</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to importing QIF format files, &kmymoney; can directly open data "
"files used by <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gnucash\">&gnucash;</link> file."
msgstr ""
"Poleg uvoza datotek formata QIF, &kmymoney; lahko neposredno odpira "
"podatkovne datoteke, ki jih uporablja datoteka <link linkend=\"details."
"impexp.gnucash\">&gnucash;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching for transactions"
msgstr "Iskanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; provides a useful and powerful transaction search facility in the "
"form of the search dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ponuja uporaben in zmogljiv pripomoček za iskanje transakcij v "
"obliki pogovornega okna za iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search dialog can be opened from the toolbar using the <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"transaction_find.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> find icon or by "
"selecting the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find "
"Transaction</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za iskanje lahko odprete v orodni vrstici z uporabo ikone za "
"iskanje <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"transaction_find.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> ali z izbiro menijske postavke <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi transakcijo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A full description of this topic can be found in the <link linkend=\"details."
"search\">Search</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Celoten opis te teme je na voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"details.search"
"\">Iskanje</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconciliation"
msgstr "Usklajevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At some point, you will want to reconcile your records and details of an "
"account with the actual account to assure they match. This is generally done "
"by comparing the account in &kmymoney; with a printed or electronic "
"statement for the account issued by the institution, such as bank, credit "
"card, loan, or any other statement. Reconciliation involves matching what "
"you have entered, specifically the transactions since the previous "
"reconciliation, with what the statement lists. If any discrepancies are "
"found, either you or the person who created the statement has made a mistake."
msgstr ""
"Na neki točki boste želeli uskladiti svoje evidence in podrobnosti o računu "
"z dejanskim računom, da zagotovite njihovo ujemanje. To običajno naredimo s "
"primerjavo računa v &kmymoney; z natisnjenim ali elektronskim izpiskom za "
"račun, ki ga izda institucija, kot je bančni izpisek, izpisek kreditne "
"kartice, posojilo ali kateri koli drug izpisek. Usklajevanje vključuje "
"ujemanje tega, kar ste vnesli, zlasti transakcij od prejšnje uskladitve, s "
"tem, kar navaja izpisek. Če so ugotovljena kakršna koli neskladja, ste se "
"zmotili vi ali oseba, ki je izpisek ustvarila."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reconcile an account, first select the account, either from the "
"<guiicon>Accounts</guiicon> View or in the <guiicon>Ledgers</guiicon> View. "
"Then, either click the <guiicon>Reconcile</guiicon> icon on the Toolbar, if "
"it is visible, or select the <menuchoice><guimenu>Account</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reconcile</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uskladiti račun, najprej izberite račun v pogledu <guiicon>Računi</"
"guiicon> ali v pogledu <guiicon>Glavne knjige</guiicon>. Nato kliknite ikono "
"<guiicon>Uskladi</guiicon> v orodni vrstici, če je vidna, ali izberite "
"postavko menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uskladi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A more detailed description of this topic can be found in the <link linkend="
"\"details.reconcile\">Reconciliation</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejši opis te teme je na voljo v razdelku <link linkend=\"details."
"reconcile\">Usklajevanje</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backing up"
msgstr "Varnostno kopiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that you have created some accounts and entered transactions it's a good "
"idea to perform a backup. Because the file used by &kmymoney; is a standard "
"&Linux; file (or &macOS; or &Windows; file, depending on your operating "
"system) you can just copy the file to another location to back it up or use "
"the dialog provided by &kmymoney;. Using the dialog is the preferred method "
"because if &kmymoney; ever starts using other file formats, such as SQL, "
"then it would be much harder to copy the file manually."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko ste ustvarili nekaj računov in vnesli transakcije, je dobro "
"narediti varnostno kopijo. Ker je datoteka, ki jo uporablja &kmymoney; "
"standardna &Linux; datoteka (ali datoteka &macOS; ali &Windows;, odvisno od "
"vašega operacijskega sistema), lahko preprosto kopirate datoteko na drugo "
"mesto, da jo varnostno kopirate, ali uporabite pogovorno okno, ki ga ponuja "
"&kmymoney;. Uporaba pogovornega okna je prednostna metoda, ker če &kmymoney; "
"kdaj začne uporabljati druge oblike zapisa datotek, kot je SQL, bi bilo "
"veliko težje kopirati datoteko ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To backup your file through &kmymoney; Select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Backup</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and enter "
"the folder where you wish the file to be saved. If the folder needs mounting "
"first and you have the sufficient privileges then check the tick box labeled "
"<guilabel>Mount this folder before backing up</guilabel> and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Za varnostno kopiranje datoteke prek &kmymoney; Izberite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Varnostno kopiranje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in vnesite mapo, v katero želite shraniti "
"datoteko. Če je treba mapo najprej namestiti in imate ustrezne privilegije, "
"potrdite polje z oznako <guilabel>Pripni to mapo pred varnostnim kopiranjem</"
"guilabel> in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file will be saved to the folder specified with the current date "
"appended to the filename so it is easy to see the date the file was backed "
"up."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka bo shranjena v določeno mapo s trenutnim datumom, dodanim k imenu "
"datoteke, tako da je enostavno videti datum, ko je bila datoteka varnostno "
"kopirana."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more details about the actual format of the data file, and the backup "
"process, see the <link linkend=\"details.formats\">File Formats</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za več podrobnosti o dejanski obliki podatkovne datoteke in postopku "
"varnostnega kopiranja glejte <link linkend=\"details.formats\">Oblike "
"datotek</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launching &kmymoney;"
msgstr "Zagon &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most commonly, you will launch &kmymoney; from an icon or a start menu of "
"your window manager or desktop environment. In this case, the default "
"behavior is that &kmymoney; will open the last file you had open. However, "
"in some circumstances, you will want or need to launch &kmymoney; from the "
"command line."
msgstr ""
"Najpogosteje boste zagnali &kmymoney; iz ikone ali začetnega menija "
"upravitelja oken ali namiznega okolja. V tem primeru je privzeto vedenje "
"&kmymoney; da bo odprl zadnjo datoteko, ki ste jo odprli. Vendar pa boste v "
"nekaterih okoliščinah želeli ali morali zagnati &kmymoney; iz ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a complete description of all the available command line options, see "
"the man page for &kmymoney;. However, there are two special cases which we "
"describe here."
msgstr ""
"Za popoln opis vseh razpoložljivih možnosti ukazne vrstice si oglejte man "
"stran za &kmymoney;. Vendar pa obstajata dva posebna primera, ki ju "
"opisujemo tukaj."

#. Tag: command
#: firsttime.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid "kmymoney -n"
msgstr "kmymoney -n"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The -n option tells &kmymoney; not to open the last file it had open. This "
"can be useful if the program crashes on startup."
msgstr ""
"Možnost -n pove &kmymoney; da ne odpre zadnje odprte datoteke. To je lahko "
"koristno, če se program ob zagonu sesuje."

#. Tag: command
#: firsttime.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid "kmymoney &lt;path to file&gt;"
msgstr "kmymoney &lt;pot do datoteke&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Giving &kmymoney; a filename on the command line tells it to open that file "
"instead of the last file it had open. You can use the name of any valid "
"&kmymoney; file, as described in the chapter on <link linkend=\"details."
"formats\">file formats</link>. In addition, this can be used to import a "
"<link linkend=\"details.impexp.gnucash\">&gnucash;</link> file."
msgstr ""
"Dajanje &kmymoney; ime datoteke v ukazni vrstici pove, naj odpre to datoteko "
"namesto zadnje odprte datoteke. Uporabite lahko ime katerega koli veljavne "
"datoteke &kmymoney;, kot je opisano v poglavju o <link linkend=\"details."
"formats\">oblikah datotek</link>. Poleg tega je to mogoče uporabiti za uvoz "
"datoteke <link linkend=\"details.impexp.gnucash\">&gnucash;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to move &kmymoney; to a new computer"
msgstr "Kako premakniti &kmymoney; na nov računalnik"

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving your data"
msgstr "Premikanje vaših podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you get a new computer, it's very easy to move your data. In fact, all "
"you have to do is to copy your &kmymoney; data file. The name of the file is "
"shown in the title bar when &kmymoney; is running; it usually ends in "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.kmy</filename>. The first time you run the "
"application on the new computer you will have to tell it where you have put "
"the data file, either by running from the command line, or from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item. You should even be able to move between &Windows;, "
"&MacOS;, and &Linux; systems."
msgstr ""
"Če dobite nov računalnik, je vaše podatke zelo enostavno premakniti. "
"Pravzaprav je vse, kar morate storiti, to, da kopirate svoj &kmymoney; "
"podatkovno datoteko. Ime datoteke je prikazano v naslovni vrstici, ko "
"&kmymoney; teče; običajno se konča s <filename class=\"extension\">.kmy</"
"filename>. Ko prvič zaženete aplikacijo v novem računalniku, ji boste morali "
"povedati, kam ste shranili podatkovno datoteko, bodisi z zagonom iz ukazne "
"vrstice ali iz elementa menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Odpri...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Mogli bi celo "
"premikati med sistemi &Windows;, &MacOS; in &Linux;."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have encrypted your data file, be sure the appropriate software and "
"keys have also been set up on the new computer."
msgstr ""
"Če ste šifrirali podatkovno datoteko, se prepričajte, da so ustrezna "
"programska oprema in ključi nastavljeni tudi na novem računalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your data is in an SQL database, refer to documentation for your database "
"software for guidance on migrating your data."
msgstr ""
"Če so vaši podatki v zbirki podatkov SQL, si oglejte dokumentacijo za "
"programsko opremo vaše baze podatkov za navodila o selitvi vaših podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that this assumes you have installed the same version of &kmymoney; on "
"the new computer as you were running on the old computer. Installing a newer "
"version should also be safe, but you need to be aware of any issues related "
"to that upgrade. Any such issues should be noted in the release notes for "
"the new version."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da to predpostavlja, da imate nameščeno isto različico "
"&kmymoney; na novem računalniku, kot ste ga izvajali na starem računalniku. "
"Tudi namestitev novejše različice bi morala biti varna, vendar se morate "
"zavedati morebitnih težav, povezanih s to nadgradnjo. Vse take težave je "
"treba zabeležiti v opombah ob izdaji za novo različico."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving your settings"
msgstr "Selitev nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:781
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you only move your data file to the new machine, as described in the "
"previous section, &kmymoney; will work correctly, but you will have lost any "
"configuration settings you changed from the default on your old machine. To "
"maintain these settings, you also need to copy your configuration file. This "
"file is called <filename>kmymoneyrc</filename>. The location of this file "
"depends on your operating system and distribution. On a &Linux; system, this "
"will most likely be <filename class=\"directory\">.config</filename> within "
"your home folder. If you are migrating from a version of &kmymoney; prior to "
"5.0, the old location was <filename class=\"directory\">.kde4</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če svojo podatkovno datoteko samo premaknete na nov računalnik, kot je "
"opisano v prejšnjem razdelku, &kmymoney; bo deloval pravilno, vendar boste "
"izgubili vse nastavitve konfiguracije, ki ste jih spremenili iz privzetih na "
"vašem starem računalniku. Če želite ohraniti te nastavitve, morate kopirati "
"tudi datoteko konfiguracije. Ta datoteka se imenuje <filename>kmymoneyrc</"
"filename>. Lokacija te datoteke je odvisna od vašega operacijskega sistema "
"in distribucije. Na siszemu &Linux;, bo to najverjetneje <filename class="
"\"directory\">.config</filename> v domači mapi. Če se selite iz različice "
"&kmymoney; pred 5.0 je bila stara lokacija <filename class=\"directory\">."
"kde4</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving plugin settings"
msgstr "Premikanje nastavitev vtičnika"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have run any &kmymoney; plugin, such as the csv importer or exporter, "
"it may also have created a configuration file in that same folder, such as "
"<filename>csvimporterrc</filename> or <filename>csvexporterrc</filename>. "
"These files should also be copied to the new computer."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zagnali vtičnika &kmymoney;, kot je uvoznik ali izvoznik csv, je "
"morda ustvaril tudi konfiguracijsko datoteko v isti mapi, kot je "
"<filename>csvimporterrc</filename> ali <filename>csvexporterrc</filename>. "
"Tudi te datoteke je treba kopirati v nov računalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with the main data file, this assumes the same version of the plugin on "
"both computers. Upgrades are generally safe, but if the functionality of the "
"plugin has changed greatly, it is advisable to carefully test using the old "
"configuration file, to be sure the plugin behaves as you expect. Of course "
"this applies even when upgrading the version of &kmymoney; on a single PC."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri glavni podatkovni datoteki, to predvideva isto različico vtičnika na "
"obeh računalnikih. Nadgradnje so na splošno varne, a če se je funkcionalnost "
"vtičnika močno spremenila, je priporočljivo skrbno preizkusiti s staro "
"konfiguracijsko datoteko, da se prepričate, da se vtičnik obnaša, kot "
"pričakujete. Seveda to velja tudi pri nadgradnji različice &kmymoney; na "
"enem računalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that when upgrading from a previous version to version 5.0 or higher, "
"the location of the template files used by the plugin for printing checks "
"has changed. Please consult the release notes or the project <ulink url="
"\"https://www.kmymoney.org/faq.php\">website</ulink> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da se je pri nadgradnji s prejšnje različice na različico 5.0 "
"ali novejšo lokacija datotek predlog, ki jih uporablja vtičnik za tiskanje "
"čekov, spremenila. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte opombe ob izdaji ali <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.kmymoney.org/faq.php\">spletno mesto</ulink> projekta."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These instructions are solely for moving your &kmymoney; data and settings. "
"However, there may be important items which are stored by &kde; and not by "
"&kmymoney;, such as passwords stored in Keychain. Moving other parts of your "
"&kde; setup is beyond the scope of this manual, although many of the "
"relevant files are also stored under <envar>$KDEHOME</envar>."
msgstr ""
"Ta navodila so namenjena izključno selitvi podatkov in nastavitev vaše "
"aplikacije &kmymoney;. Vendar pa lahko obstajajo pomembni elementi, ki so "
"shranjeni v &kde; in ne v &kmymoney;, kot so gesla, shranjena v Keychainu. "
"Selitve drugih delov nastavitev vašega &kde; namizja presega obseg tega "
"priročnika, čeprav je veliko ustreznih datotek shranjenih tudi pod <envar>"
"$KDEHOME</envar>."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Help / Contacting the Developers / Reporting Bugs"
msgstr "Pridobivanje pomoči / Stik z razvijalci / Prijava napak"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since support channels change over time, you can refer to the <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/support.html\">Support page</ulink> at the <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/\">&kmymoney; web site</ulink> for the most up-to-"
"date information on where to get help with &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Ker se kanali podpore sčasoma spreminjajo, se lahko obrnete na <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/support.html\">stran za podporo</ulink> na <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org /\">spletno mesto &kmymoney;</ulink> za najnovejše "
"informacije o tem, kje poiskati pomoč pri &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you simply have questions about using &kmymoney;, you want to confirm you "
"understanding of how the application works, or need assistance figuring out "
"the best way to handle a particular financial situation, please consider "
"using one of the information sources, forums, mailing lists, or chat "
"channels listed at the above link."
msgstr ""
"Če imate samo vprašanja o uporabi &kmymoney;, želite potrditi, da razumete, "
"kako aplikacija deluje, ali potrebujete pomoč pri iskanju najboljšega načina "
"za reševanje določene finančne situacije, razmislite o uporabi enega od "
"virov informacij, forumov, poštnih seznamov ali kanale za klepet, navedene "
"na zgornji povezavi."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contacting the developers"
msgstr "Stik z razvijalci"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For general questions or comments about &kmymoney;, there is a users' "
"mailing list &userlist; with more details <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/"
"mailman/listinfo/kmymoney\">here</ulink>. This list is suitable for general "
"questions and discussion. There is also a developers' mailing list &devlist; "
"with more details <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/"
"kmymoney-devel\">here</ulink>. This list is intended for more technical "
"discussions. Since replies are often sent only to the list, you may not get "
"any response unless you subscribe to the list you send to."
msgstr ""
"Za splošna vprašanja ali komentarje o &kmymoney; je na voljo poštni seznam "
"uporabnikov &userlist; z več podrobnostmi <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/"
"mailman/listinfo/kmymoney\">tukaj</ulink>. Ta seznam je primeren za splošna "
"vprašanja in razprave. Obstaja tudi poštni seznam razvijalcev &devlist; z "
"več podrobnostmi <ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kmymoney-"
"devel\">tukaj</ulink>. Ta seznam je namenjen bolj tehničnim razpravam. Ker "
"so odgovori pogosto poslani samo na seznam, morda ne boste prejeli nobenega "
"odgovora, razen če se naročite na seznam, na katerega pošiljate."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the developers generally monitor the various contact channels "
"mentioned above, so direct email contact is rarely necessary. However, we're "
"happy to hear about your experiences using &kmymoney; over whatever channel "
"you prefer."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da razvijalci na splošno spremljajo različne zgoraj omenjene "
"kontaktne kanale, zato je neposreden e-poštni stik redko potreben. Vendar "
"smo veseli vaših izkušenj z &kmymoney; prek katerega koli kanala vam je "
"ljubše."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reporting bugs"
msgstr "Poročanje o napakah"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To report a bug please use the interface provided by &kmymoney; by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item and filling in the required information. However, in "
"case you have any difficulties with that method, you can report a bug (or "
"file a wish-list or enhancement request) directly at the <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org\">&kde; bug reporting web site</ulink>. Reports "
"should be filed against the product <quote>kmymoney</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prijaviti napako, uporabite vmesnik &kmymoney; tako, da izberete "
"element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi "
"napako</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in izpolnite zahtevane informacije. Če pa "
"imate kakršne koli težave s to metodo, lahko prijavite napako (ali vložite "
"seznam želja ali zahtevo za izboljšavo) neposredno na <ulink url=\"https://"
"bugs.kde.org\">&kde; spletno mesto za poročanje o napakah</ulink>. Prijave "
"je treba vložiti zoper izdelek <quote>kmymoney</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In any case, before reporting a bug, please read through the guidelines "
"below. Following them will make it more likely that the developers will be "
"able to quickly identify the problem without having to ask you for more "
"information. Also try to be sure that what you are reporting really is a bug "
"(or wishlist/enhancement request.) If things are just not working they way "
"you expect, or you need help using some feature of &kmymoney;, please use "
"one of the alternate support channels listed above."
msgstr ""
"V vsakem primeru, preden prijavite napako, preberite spodnje smernice. Če "
"jih upoštevate, bo večja verjetnost, da bodo lahko razvijalci hitro "
"prepoznali težavo, ne da bi vas morali prositi za več informacij. "
"Prepričajte se tudi, da je to, kar sporočate, res napaka (ali seznam želja/"
"zahteva za izboljšavo.) Če stvari preprosto ne delujejo tako, kot ste "
"pričakovali, ali potrebujete pomoč pri uporabi nekaterih funkcij &kmymoney;, "
"prosimo uporabite enega od nadomestnih podpornih kanalov, navedenih zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing High Quality Bug Reports"
msgstr "Pisanje visokokakovostnih poročil o napakah"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We encourage users to take extra time to write high-quality bug reports when "
"submitting them. This reduces wasted effort on all sides, as the reporter "
"and the developer who will fix it trade emails until this information is "
"really in place."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnike spodbujamo, da si ob oddaji vzamejo več časa za pisanje "
"visokokakovostnih poročil o napakah. To zmanjša izgubljen trud na vseh "
"straneh, saj poročevalec in razvijalec, ki bo to popravil, izmenjujeta e-"
"poštna sporočila, dokler te informacije res niso na mestu."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eli Goldberg wrote the canonical Bug-Writing Guideline, available at <ulink "
"url=\"https://issues.apache.org/bugwritinghelp.html\">https://issues.apache."
"org/bugwritinghelp.html</ulink>. Generally, you'll be well-served by "
"following the guidelines and advice from that page. Some of those points are "
"repeated below:"
msgstr ""
"Eli Goldberg je napisal kanonične smernice za opisovanje programskih napak "
"(hroščev), ki so na voljo na <ulink url=\"https://issues.apache.org/"
"bugwritinghelp.html\">https://issues.apache.org/bugwritinghelp.html</ulink>. "
"Na splošno vam bo dobro služilo, če boste upoštevali smernice in nasvete s "
"te strani. Nekatere od teh točk so ponovljene spodaj:"

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include your system information"
msgstr "Vključite informacije o sistemu"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item will fill this in automatically, but if "
"you would prefer not to use this interface, there are several items you need "
"to include in the report. We will need to know what operating system you are "
"using (&Linux;, &MacOS;, or &Windows;), the version of &kde;, and the "
"version of &kmymoney; you're running, and either the version of &MacOS; or "
"&Windows; or the name and version of your &Linux; distribution and the "
"version of your kernel. This information is extremely important, as many "
"bugs (as well as behaviors mis-identified as bugs) depend on the Operating "
"System."
msgstr ""
"Element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi "
"napako</guimenuitem></menuchoice> bo to samodejno izpolnil, če pa tega "
"vmesnika ne želite uporabljati, potrebujete več elementov vključiti v "
"poročilo. Vedeti moramo, kateri operacijski sistem uporabljate (&Linux;, "
"&MacOS; ali &Windows;), različico &kde; in različico &kmymoney; ki ga "
"uporabljate, in različica &MacOS; ali &Windows; ali ime in različico vaše "
"&Linux; distribucije in različico vašega jedra. Te informacije so izjemno "
"pomembne, saj je veliko hroščev (pa tudi vedenj, napačno prepoznanih kot "
"hrošči) odvisnih od operacijskega sistema."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include a backtrace for crashes"
msgstr "Vključite povratno sled za sesutja"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The backtrace is often the single most useful piece of information in "
"solving crashes."
msgstr ""
"Povratna sled je pogosto najbolj uporaben podatek pri reševanju sesutij."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to reproduce it"
msgstr "Poskusite ga reproducirati"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let us know if you were able to do so. It's useful to know whether the bug "
"only happened once and you couldn't get it to happen again or if it happens "
"every time or if it happens sometimes but not others."
msgstr ""
"Sporočite nam, če vam je to uspelo. Koristno je vedeti, ali se je napaka "
"pojavila le enkrat in je niste mogli doseči, da bi se ponovila, ali se zgodi "
"vsakič ali pa se zgodi včasih, drugič pa ne."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:930
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include specific steps"
msgstr "Vključite posebne korake"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a bad bug report: <quote>I entered a transaction, and &kmymoney; "
"crashed.</quote> A much better bug report is: <quote>Using the transaction "
"form, I entered a new transaction in my Credit Card account. I selected the "
"Transfer tab, entered an amount, then changed to the Deposit tab, and back "
"to the Transfer tab. When I returned to the Transfer tab, &kmymoney; "
"crashed. This bug is fully reproducible for me.</quote>"
msgstr ""
"To je slabo poročilo o napaki: <quote>Vnesel sem transakcijo in &kmymoney; "
"se je sesul.</quote> Veliko boljše poročilo o napaki je: <quote>Z uporabo "
"obrazca za transakcije sem vnesel novo transakcijo na svoj račun kreditne "
"kartice. Izbral sem zavihek Prenos, vnesel znesek, nato prešel na zavihek "
"Depozit in nazaj na zavihek Prenos. Ko sem se vrnil na zavihek Prenos, se je "
"&kmymoney; sesul. Ta hrošč je zame popolnoma ponovljiv.</quote>"

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tell us what you expected to happen"
msgstr "Povejte nam, kaj ste pričakovali, da se bo zgodilo"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some cases, this is obvious, but in more subtle bugs, sometimes you'll "
"see a bug report where it is not obvious what the reporter expected to "
"happen. Always tell us what you think should have happened, as well as what "
"did happen."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih primerih je to očitno, toda pri bolj subtilnih napakah boste "
"včasih videli poročilo o napaki, kjer ni očitno, kaj je prijavitelj "
"pričakoval, da se bo zgodilo. Vedno nam povejte, kaj mislite, da bi se "
"moralo zgoditi, pa tudi, kaj se je zgodilo."

#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Consider running with debugging enabled"
msgstr "Razmislite o izvajanju z omogočenim odpravljanjem napak"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By compiling a version configured with --enable-debug=full you can ensure "
"that the best possible backtraces are generated. If you encounter a crash, "
"run &kmymoney; again from within gdb, and reproduce the crash. When it "
"crashes, type <quote>bt</quote> to generate a backtrace."
msgstr ""
"S prevajanjem različice, konfigurirane z --enable-debug=full, lahko "
"zagotovite, da so ustvarjene najboljše možne povratne sledi. Če naletite na "
"sesutje, zaženite &kmymoney; znova iz gdb in ponovite sesutje. Ko se sesuje, "
"vnesite <quote>bt</quote>, da ustvarite povratno sled."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Running this way is a bit more difficult, so we don't expect all users to do "
"this. However, if you're interested in helping &kmymoney; become as stable "
"as possible, this is the best way to do it short of finding the bug in the "
"code and sending in a patch."
msgstr ""
"Izvajanje na ta način je nekoliko težje, zato ne pričakujemo, da bodo to "
"storili vsi uporabniki. Vendar, če želite pomagati, da &kmymoney; postane "
"čim bolj stabilen, je to najboljši način, da to storite, če ne poiščete "
"hrošča v kodi in pošljete popravka."

